name: Chinese zodiac series (dog)
description:
The dog zodiac is one of the 12 zodiac signs in the Chinese calendar.

According to Chinese beliefs, people who have a dog zodiac are people who are very loyal, honest, and trustworthy, but can also be patient and caring. They are leaders, hard workers, dedicated so often successful in large-scale business.

Dogs are the zodiac sign for those born in 1958, 1970, 1982, 1994, 2006, 2018, and other multiples of 12.
